title: Stargate Universe S03E01 Forever Voyaging Fan Photonovel
description:
Stargate Universe returns in the fan-created photonovel "Forever Voyaging", which continues the story into season 3 using over 140 photographs from the show and elsewhere. For all who've wondered what happened to Eli and his stasis pod, this is for you!

Also included are the complete ebook "Hey Netflix! Save Stargate Universe!" and the short pro-SGU videos "Are You a Dog?" and "30 Second Personality Test".

Please help save SGU by SEEDING this torrent! Millions of SGU viewers worldwide weren't counted in the ratings because we don't watch traditional TV networks. If we can make a BitTorrent swarm that rivals Game of Thrones, then MGM and the online networks WILL sit up and take notice!

Thanks! Share and enjoy!

--Blake Linton
